products.title: Sahara Pvc Blackout Ivory 89mm Vertical Blind
products.description: Their sahara pvc blackout range is available in two classic and neutral tones that are ideal for wet or heat based environments. This hard-wearing cream pvc vertical blind is ideal for areas where it is exposed to heat or wet as it is flame retardent and waterproof.
